rows.label: tlk42300116_01_msg0001
rows.name:
Quiet day again. No customers.
Mochimochi getting bored out of head.

rows.label: tlk42300116_01_msg0002
rows.name: From looks of you... You salvager?

rows.label: tlk42300116_01_msg0005
rows.name:
It nothing! Forget Mochimochi say
anything!

rows.label: tlk42300116_01_msg0006
rows.name:
Sorry, probably not very interesting
to talk to Mochimochi. Not much to talk
about.

rows.label: tlk42300116_01_msg0007
rows.name:
Mochimochi just get excited at sight of
salvagers doing business.
